collections.name: "Virgin Visions: Unseen Realities"
collections.description:
This collection reflects my inner world and personal experiences as an adult, virgin woman. Through an honest and unfiltered perspective on body, gender, and emotions, I aim to express art from a unique and pure viewpoint. Virginity offers a raw, unrefined view of life’s complexities, feminine identity, and human emotions, all of which are vividly portrayed in these works.

These portraits blend beauty and ugliness, joy and fear, and contradictions, intertwining to capture the human experience from a psychological perspective. My goal is to explore life’s complexities and my feminine identity, inviting viewers to embark on a deep, introspective journey through the works.

These images are not only reflections of my thoughts and emotions but also a raw, forgotten experience where body, mind, and emotions intertwine unmediated. The works immerse the viewer in an inner world where beauty, contradiction, and the search for identity merge together.

collections.name: Painting Music
collections.description: My most recent commissions have been to create visuals for classical music concerts. In these works I created moving image sequences using my own paintings, projected onto huge LED walls, in dialogue with the music. This inspired me to think further about my moving images and to create my first NFT works. As painting to music has always been at the root of my work, the NFTs were inspired by musical works. The material and the power of manual work play an important role in my creations, so I created the NFTs by working with my manual works. The Ode to Joy NFTs were created for Beethoven's Ode to Joy. artist: Viktória Nagy www.viktorianagy.com

collections.name: The Cappys
collections.description:
Welcome to "The Cappys", a whimsical and heartwarming NFT collection celebrating the world's chillest creature—the Capybara! Each unique artwork captures the charm, humor, and versatility of these adorable animals, showcasing them in a variety of imaginative settings, from tropical beaches to futuristic cities.

With themes spanning seasonal vibes, fantasy worlds, cultural tributes, and quirky professions, "The Cappys" invites you into a universe where Capybaras live their best lives. Whether they're rocking sunglasses on a yacht, donning a wizard's robe, or simply relaxing with their animal friends, these lovable creatures bring joy and creativity to your NFT portfolio.

Embrace the fun, share the chill, and join the Capybara craze with "The Cappys"—a collection as diverse and delightful as the creatures themselves. Perfect for collectors who appreciate charm, personality, and a little bit of capy-magic!

collections.name: Chonky Pandas
collections.description:
Chonky Pandas is a distinctive NFT collection that brings together the cuteness of chubby pandas with the elegance of traditional Chinese attire from various dynasties. Each panda wears a carefully designed outfit that reflects the unique fashion trends of a particular era, from the grandeur of the Tang Dynasty to the imperial splendor of the Qing Dynasty. These pandas are not just adorable but also represent the timeless beauty and rich cultural heritage of China.

With every new release, collectors can discover a fresh, playful take on royal Chinese fashion, blending art and history. Whether adorned in intricate silk robes, opulent accessories, or elegant hairstyles, each panda is a charming tribute to the elegance and artistry of ancient China, reimagined for a modern, fun world.

collections.name: Cello & Electronics Vol. 1 (2018-2024) by Nicholas Denton Protsack
collections.description:
An anthology of original works for cello and electronic media by composer-cellist Nicholas Denton Protsack. Released between 2018 and 2024.

About the artist:
BMI Award-winning composer-cellist, Nicholas Denton Protsack (b. 1994), strives to unify music and environment. Called a "(composer) to keep a close eye on" by the Canadian Music Centre, Nicholas works in notated mediums, recorded mediums, and improvisational frameworks. His music is frequently performed in North America, Europe, and New Zealand.

https://www.dentonprotsack.com/

collections.name: NBORN
collections.description:
NBORN

NBORN is a captivating collection of digital art that explores the theme of cosmic creation. Each piece features a glowing, iridescent egg floating in the vastness of space, surrounded by a starry void and distant nebulae. The egg, shimmering in hues of silver, violet, gold, and midnight blue, is adorned with intricate glowing patterns, evoking a sense of mystery and wonder.

This collection is a celebration of beauty, energy, and the unknown, inviting viewers to immerse themselves in a visually stunning and otherworldly experience. NBORN is not just a series of images—it is a journey into the depths of cosmic imagination, where art meets the infinite.
